{"url": "https://www.ics.uci.edu/~kobsa/courses/ICS104/course-notes/metaphors.htm", "content": "<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC \"-//w3c//dtd html 4.0 transitional//en\">\n<html>\n  <head>\n    <meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html;\n      charset=windows-1252\">\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"css/lightbox.css\" type=\"text/css\"\n      media=\"screen\">\n    <script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"js/prototype.js\"></script>\n    <script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"js/scriptaculous.js?load=effects,builder\"></script>\n    <script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"js/lightbox.js\"></script>\n    <meta name=\"GENERATOR\" content=\"Mozilla/4.72 (Macintosh; I; PPC)\n      [Netscape]\">\n    <title>Important HCI metaphors</title>\n  </head>\n  <body style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">\n    <p><font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\"><font size=\"+4\" face=\"Arial,\n          Helvetica, sans-serif\">Important HCI\n          metaphors</font></font> <font face=\"Arial, Helvetica,\n        sans-serif\"><br>\n        &nbsp; </font></p>\n    <p><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\"><b><font size=\"+2\">Interface\nmetaphors\n            evoke an <i>initial</i> mental model in users of the\n            system's structure and operation. Metaphors should relate to\n            users'\n            past experiences and should <font face=\"Arial, Helvetica,\n              sans-serif\"><b>be\n                consistent</b></font>.</font></b> </font></p>\n    <ul>\n      <li><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"5\"><b>(Typewriter\n              metaphor):</b></font><font size=\"+3\"> </font><font\n            size=\"+2\">Evoked\n            easily due to physical similarities. Should be avoided</font></font></li>\n      <li><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"5\"><b>Desktop\n              metaphor:</b></font><font size=\"+3\"> </font><font\n            size=\"+2\">Once the most important metaphor, now slowly\n            disappearing.</font></font></li>\n      <li><b><font size=\"5\" face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\">Book\n            metaphor:</font></b><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica,\n          sans-serif\"><font size=\"+3\"> </font><font size=\"+2\">For <a\n              href=\"bookmetaphor.jpg\" rel=\"lightbox\" title=\"Book\n              metaphor for hypertext\">hypertext</a>,\n            online </font></font><a href=\"book-metaphor-small.m4v\"><font\n            size=\"5\" face=\"Arial,Helvetica\">catalogues</font></a><font\n          size=\"5\" face=\"Arial,Helvetica\"> <small>(5.8MB)</small><br>\n        </font></li>\n      <p> </p>\n      <li><b><font size=\"5\" face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\">Filing\n            cabinets </font></b>\n        <ul>\n          <li><font size=\"5\" face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\">for\n              online\n              documentation, <a href=\"shopping-site-tabs.jpg\"\n                rel=\"lightbox\" title=\"Index cards metaphor\">subdivisions</a>\n              in web offerings, <a href=\"filing-cabinet.jpg\"\n                rel=\"lightbox\" title=\"Index card metaphor (with multiple\n                rows)\">system settings</a> </font></li>\n          <li><font size=\"5\" face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\">orientation\nproblems\n              with tabs that have more than one level <a\n                href=\"two-level-tabs.m4v\"><font face=\"Wingdings\"><img\n                    style=\"border: 0px solid ; width: 21px; height:\n                    27px;\" alt=\"Thumb pointing down\"\n                    src=\"../../../graphics/thumb_down-small.png\"><br>\n                </font></a> </font></li>\n        </ul>\n      </li>\n      <br>\n      <li><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"5\"><b>Office\n              metaphor:</b></font><font size=\"+3\"> </font><font\n            size=\"+2\">For\n            collections of documents </font><a\n            href=\"juliegarwood1209.swf\"><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica,\n              sans-serif\"> <font size=\"4\" face=\"Arial, Helvetica,\n                sans-serif\"><font size=\"5\" face=\"Wingdings\"><img\n                    style=\"border: 0px solid ; width: 21px; height:\n                    27px;\" alt=\"Thumb pointing down\"\n                    src=\"../../../graphics/thumb_down-small.png\"></font></font></font></a></font></li>\n      <li><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"5\"><b><a\n                href=\"hackers.jpg\" rel=\"lightbox\" title=\"Library\n                metaphor\">Library\n                metaphor</a>:</b></font><font size=\"+2\">\n            For large collections of documents</font></font></li>\n      <li><b><font size=\"5\"><a href=\"virtual-environment.jpg\"\n              rel=\"lightbox\"><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\">Building\n                metaphors</font></a></font></b>&nbsp;<font size=\"5\"><font\n            face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\"><a href=\"foyer.swf\"><font\n                face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"4\"\n                  face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"5\"\n                    face=\"Wingdings\"></font></font></font></a><font\n              face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"4\"\n                face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"5\"\n                  face=\"Wingdings\"><a target=\"_blank\"><img\n                      style=\"border: 0px solid ; width: 21px; height:\n                      27px;\" alt=\"Link to archived version of\n                      Brillpublications.com\"\n                      src=\"../../../graphics/thumb_down-small.png\"></a></font></font></font><b>,\n            </b><a href=\"city-metaphor.jpg\" rel=\"lightbox\" title=\"City\n              metaphor\"><strong>city\n                metaphors</strong></a>,</font></font><font size=\"5\"\n          face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\"> etc.<b>:</b></font><font\n          face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"+3\"> </font><font\n            size=\"+2\">for virtual worlds</font></font></li>\n      <li><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"+2\"><a\n              style=\"font-weight: bold;\" href=\"traffic-metaphor.png\">Traffic\n              metaphor</a><br>\n          </font></font></li>\n      <li><b><font size=\"5\"><a href=\"agents.jpg\" rel=\"lightbox\"\n              title=\"Animated agents metaphor\"><font face=\"Arial,\n                Helvetica, sans-serif\">Animated agent metaphor</font></a></font><font\n            size=\"5\" face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\">:</font></b><font\n          face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"+3\"> </font><font\n            size=\"+2\">for <a href=\"agent-guidance.mov\">guidance</a>,\n            recommendation, <a href=\"persuasion.mov\">persuasion</a><br>\n          </font></font></li>\n      <li><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"+3\"><b><font\n                size=\"5\">Composite metaphors</font></b></font></font><br>\n        <font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"+2\">Combine\n            2\n            or more metaphors (like office, file cabinet and desktop)</font></font>\n      </li>\n    </ul>\n    <table width=\"746\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"1\">\n      <tbody>\n        <tr>\n          <td width=\"49\"><img\n              src=\"../../../graphics/pointing-finger-right.jpg\"\n              width=\"97\" height=\"69\"></td>\n          <td width=\"691\"><font size=\"5\" face=\"Arial, Helvetica,\n              sans-serif\"><i>The\n                learning and retention of a system's functionality\n                is considerably facilitated\n                by meaningful and consistent metaphors. </i><font\n                size=\"5\" face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font\n                  size=\"6\" face=\"Wingdings\"><img style=\"border: 0px\n                    solid ; width: 21px; height: 27px;\"\n                    src=\"../../../graphics/thumb_down-small.png\"\n                    alt=\"The video shows a user clicking on tabs which\n                    don't work as expected (they rather work as sequence\n                    indicators)\"></font></font><a\n                href=\"tab-metaphor-violation.mov\">&#9785;</a> <font size=\"5\"\n                face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"6\"\n                  face=\"Wingdings\"><a href=\"wrong-tabs-methaphor.jpg\"\n                    rel=\"lightbox\" title=\"Inappropriate use of metaphor\"><img\n                      src=\"../../../graphics/thumb_down-small.png\"\n                      width=\"21\" height=\"27\" border=\"0\"></a></font></font></font><font\n              size=\"5\" face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</font>\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n      </tbody>\n    </table>\n    <p><font size=\"5\" face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\"><i>&nbsp; </i></font></p>\n  </body>\n</html>\n", "encoding": "ascii"}